{"tid":1467722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DLLM 咩叫核彈都唔割！全部同我入來","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:39:04.000Z","uid":102005,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0baef99faefdca4ec4c404879f449ca94ca225d6","tid":1467722,"uid":102005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌哂你地老母<br />\n全部post 都怪前線失控</span></span><br />\n冇企過係前線嘅你，冇資格怪人<br />\n企前線所面對嘅恐懼、壓力，不足為外人道也<br />\n佢哋到今時今日先爆係極度克制<br />\n受過專業訓練嘅克警失控左好撚耐<br />\n佢地係人，有感情。<br />\n我地和理非核彈都唔割，鏡頭出左街就幫佢救<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑社會出來打斬人<br />\n班友二話不說過哂去保護香港市民<br />\n同黑社會打，你估佢唔驚呀，頂硬上咋<br />\n<br />\n永遠珍惜啲班手足！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地俾人帶梗風向呀<br />\n請聽我以下講嘅野做文宣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">和理非話前線失控<br />\n係！ 咁又點？<br />\nDon&rsquo;t Blame the Victim!<br />\n請諗下<br />\n邊個安排25 <br />\n邊個不停武力鎮壓<br />\n邊個射爆人隻眼<br />\n邊個拘捕人後打到人腦出血</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係政權逼到我地前線失控! 槍頭對準政權!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"adf528865924edb70e10b6215a7d9225e0d3c784","tid":1467722,"uid":102005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:29.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"c8311d856382dcb215a142b2274c3f856229d6ed","tid":1467722,"uid":102005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048f1a22cbc558909764d76bb61ebfe2aef70ecd","tid":1467722,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:24.000Z","msg":"我哋全部疑心生暗鬼自亂晒陣腳, 呢個內部問題要諗方法處理, 總之呢個moment抽離一下冷靜一下唔好俾仇恨情緒同失敗主義支配自己"},{"pid":"bd53c87be34ecdc21142833ab8608571651d129e","tid":1467722,"uid":102005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"